            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_188gc' title='Col. 188GC &mdash; HL Deb 04 May 2004 vol 660 c188GC' name='column_188gc' href='#column_188gc' rel='bookmark'>188GC</a>
            point. Criminals guilty of far more serious crimes have often been caught out by the most minor motoring offences.
          </p>
