          <p class='first-para'>
            The Judicial Appointments Authority.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0660P0-04175'>
        <a name='S5LV0660P0_20040504_GCR_133'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-william-astor' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0660P0_20040504_GCR_133' title='Link to this speech by Mr William Astor' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-william-astor" title="Mr William Astor">Viscount Astor</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            Well, there we are. I do not know whether the Minister has just made an important ministerial announcement. I am grateful for his reply. I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0660P0-04176'>
