            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_218gc' title='Col. 218GC &mdash; HL Deb 04 May 2004 vol 660 c218GC' name='column_218gc' href='#column_218gc' rel='bookmark'>218GC</a>
            authority or the national authorities. So it is very beneficial. As I said, the crucial point is that a speed camera that picks up no one speeding is successful.
          </p>
