            120 miles per hour? Technology has developed apace, and I am sure that the noble Lord's new car now has airbags, which would provide considerably greater safety. In the days of old, if a driver crashed a Morris Minor the engine went straight through the compartment and the steering wheel straight through the driver. We have moved on from those days.
          </p>
