      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0660P0-04345'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0660P0_20040504_GCR_303' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 94 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0660P0-04346'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0660P0_20040504_GCR_304' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Schedule 12 [<span class="italic">Repeals</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0660P0-04347'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0660P0_20040504_GCR_305' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="bold">Lord Evans of Temple Guiting</span> moved Amendment No. 128A:
        <q>Page 89, column 2, leave out line 14.</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0660P0-04348'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0660P0_20040504_GCR_306' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        On Question, amendment agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0660P0-04349'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0660P0_20040504_GCR_307' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Schedule 12, as amended, agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0660P0-04350'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0660P0_20040504_GCR_308' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clauses 95 and 96 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0660P0-04351'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0660P0_20040504_GCR_309' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        In the Title:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0660P0-04352'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0660P0_20040504_GCR_310' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        [<span class="italic">Amendment No. 129 not moved</span>.]
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0660P0-04353'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0660P0_20040504_GCR_311' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Title agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0660P0-04354'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0660P0_20040504_GCR_312' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Bill reported with amendments.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0660P0-04355'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0660P0_20040504_GCR_313' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The Committee adjourned at four minutes past seven o'clock.
      </p>
